.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: chinese, turkish, japanese, australian, nigerian, brazilian, russian
7 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, ferret, goldfish, bird, mouse, snake
 1. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 3. the owner of the bird is the russian##1
 4. the japanese is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 6. the australian is the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the chinese is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the snake and the australian##2
 9. the chinese is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the turkish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | russian | nigerian | chinese | turkish   | australian | japanese | brazilian |
| Pet           | bird | mouse     | hedgehog     | ferret | goldfish   | frog   | snake    |

