.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, mirinda, soy-milk, 7up, cola, hot-chocolate
There are 7 different nationalities: spanish, italian, turkish, argentine, russian, dutch, brazilian
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the turkish##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the russian##1
 3. the dutch is on the right of the argentine##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the russian##1
 5. the spanish is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the argentine is between the person drinking mirinda and the dutch##2
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
 8. the argentine is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the italian##1
10. the spanish is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | 7up  | soy-milk  | almond-milk  | hot-chocolate      | cola       | coffee |
| Nationality   | russian | argentine | dutch | brazilian | spanish | turkish | italian  |

