.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, ambient, gospel, d&b, salsa, soul
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, snowmobile, taxi, trike, scooter, boat
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the trike is the fan of r&b##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the fan of soul and the fan of jazz##2
4. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
8. the person driving the quad-bike is the fan of gospel##1
9. the fan of d&b is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel      | d&b | jazz | ambient | soul      | r&b      | salsa |
| Transport     | quad-bike | scooter | boat       | jet-ski | snowmobile | trike | taxi |

