.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  engineer, designer, dressmaker, freelancer, fisherman, coach, software-developer
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, skateboarding, biathlon, baseball, skiing, rugby
1. the dressmaker is on the left of the software-developer##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the fisherman##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the designer is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the coach is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who's sport is baseball and the engineer##2
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
8. the coach is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | fisherman | engineer | freelancer | coach | designer | dressmaker     | software-developer |
| Sport   | skateboarding   | biathlon    | rugby    | baseball      | swimming  | soccer | skiing |

