.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, sprite, juice, 7up, almond-milk, soy-milk
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey, weightlifting, tennis, swimming, baseball, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person drinking 7up##2
10. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | water    | juice | sprite   | almond-milk | soy-milk    | 7up |
| Sport      | tennis | climbing | snowboarding    | ice-hockey | swimming    | weightlifting | baseball  |

