The people have 7 different jobs:  nurse, electrician, freelancer, doctor, bartender, videographer, paramedic
 1. the bartender is on the left of the doctor##1
 2. the nurse is on the left of the freelancer##1
 3. the videographer is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the bartender is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 7. the electrician is on the right of the videographer##1
 8. the nurse is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking milk##2
11. the bartender is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | tea  | soy-milk   | milk         | sprite     | almond-milk              | 7up    | iced-tea     |
| Job        | videographer | electrician | bartender | doctor | paramedic | nurse | freelancer |

