.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, mystery, zombie, scientific, comedy, time-travel, documentary
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, subway, car, train, roller, van, ship
1. the person watching spy movies is the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is between the person driving the ship and the person driving the roller##2
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
9. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific     | time-travel | comedy | zombie | documentary  | spy |
| Transport     | car | train | roller   | bike     | ship    | subway | van   |

