.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, almond-milk, water, lemonade, sprite, juice
The people have 7 different hobbies: dancing, collecting, reading, drawing, traveling, card-games, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person drinking water is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate       | juice         | lemonade         | water   | almond-milk        | sprite |
| Hobby      | woodworking | reading | dancing | traveling | collecting | card-games | drawing  |

