5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
7. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | baking       | skydiving    | collecting | chess | dancing     | gardening       |
