.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: thriller, family, mystery, comedy, crime, disaster, fantasy
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: r&b, blues, trance, jazz, soul, rock, indie
 1. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of indie##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 3. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the fan of r&b##2
 4. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching crime movies##2
 5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is the fan of soul##1
 9. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
10. the fan of jazz is the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | thriller | family  | crime   | disaster | fantasy | mystery |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | indie       | r&b | trance | rock  | blues   | soul   |

