 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 6. the person eating asparagus is the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person drinking eggplantade is the person eating watermelon##1
 8. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person eating asparagus##2
10. the person drinking eggplantade is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
