 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person eating plum is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is the person eating lettuce##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating kale##1
10. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | coffee       | tea | almond-milk      | soy-milk | juice       | 7up | sprite |
